      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/al-kafi:5:3:124:2",
      "text": [
        " سَأَلْتُ أَبَا عَبْدِ اللَّهِ ( عليه السلام ) عَنِ الْأَمَةِ تُبَاعُ وَ لَهَا زَوْجٌ فَقَالَ صَفْقَتُهَا طَلَاقُهَا ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Ali Bin Ibrahim, from his father, from Hammad Bin Isa, from Rabie Bin Abdullah, from Abdul Rahman Bin Abu Abdullah who said, ",
          "‘I asked Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> about the slave girl who is sold and for her is a husband. So he<sup>asws</sup> said: ‘Her take-over is her divorce’."
        ]
      }
    },
